### 18. IVR behavior

Default IVR behavior:

```text
Pick up either phone:
  ATA off-hook auto-dials 700
  FreeSWITCH answers with the IVR

Press 1:
  Calls the other phone

Press 2:
  Runs relay_raise_command
  Expected command: sudo disco-relay raise 10 40

Press 3:
  Runs relay_lower_command
  Expected command: sudo disco-relay lower 10 60

Press 9:
  Hidden/admin option to record a new greeting
```

FreeSWITCH should use `bgsystem`, not `bg_system`, for relay commands:

```xml
<action application="bgsystem" data="$${relay_raise_command}"/>
<action application="bgsystem" data="$${relay_lower_command}"/>
```

