  ipv4.never-default no
Disable IP forwarding

The Pi should not route the ATA network out through Wi-Fi.

sudo tee /etc/sysctl.d/98-bella-no-routing.conf >/dev/null <<'EOF'
net.ipv4.ip_forward = 0
net.ipv6.conf.all.forwarding = 0
EOF

sudo sysctl --system

Expected:

