dnsmasq DHCP server on eth0 only

The Pi provides DHCP only to the Grandstream ATA network.

sudo tee /etc/dnsmasq.d/bella-ata.conf >/dev/null <<'EOF'
interface=eth0
bind-dynamic
except-interface=wlan0

port=0

dhcp-authoritative
dhcp-range=192.168.50.100,192.168.50.150,255.255.255.0,12h

# Do not advertise default gateway or DNS.
